<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error - NeuroCare AI</title>
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-body-bg text-primary-dark font-outfit antialiased">

    <!-- Minimal Navbar -->
    <nav class="glass-nav fixed top-0 left-0 w-full py-3.5 z-50">
        <div class="page-container-wide flex items-center justify-between">
            <a class="brand-link" href="/" aria-label="NeuroCare AI — Beranda">
                <img src="/images/neurocare-icon.png" alt="" class="brand-logo-mark" width="32" height="32">
                <span class="brand-logo-text">NeuroCare <span class="brand-logo-ai">AI</span></span>
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-secondary-blue transition-all flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <i class="bi bi-house"></i> Kembali ke Home
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-5 pt-16">
        <div class="max-w-lg w-full">

            <!-- Error Card -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-medium p-8 text-center">

                <!-- Icon -->
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-rose-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 border border-rose-100">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill text-rose-500 text-4xl"></i>
                </div>

                <!-- Error Content -->
                <span class="inline-block bg-rose-50 text-rose-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider border border-rose-100 mb-4">
                    Terjadi Kesalahan
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                    <%= error || 'Terjadi Kesalahan' %>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-5 leading-relaxed">
                    <%= message || 'Terjadi kesalahan yang tidak terduga.' %>
                </p>

                <% if (details) { %>
                <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6 text-left">
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Detail Teknis</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 font-mono leading-relaxed break-all"><%= details %></p>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <!-- Action Buttons -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center mb-6">
                    <a href="/predict" class="btn-primary-gradient py-2.5 px-6 rounded-xl text-sm inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Kembali ke Form
                    </a>
                    <a href="/" class="btn-outline-custom py-2.5 px-6 rounded-xl text-sm inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-house"></i> Halaman Utama
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Troubleshooting Steps -->
            <div class="mt-5 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm p-5">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="bi bi-tools text-secondary-blue"></i> Langkah Pemecahan Masalah
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-secondary-blue text-[10px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Pastikan Python API berjalan</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Jalankan <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">python predict_api.py</code> di terminal terpisah.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-secondary-blue text-[10px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Verifikasi koneksi MySQL (XAMPP)</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Pastikan Apache dan MySQL di XAMPP sudah aktif dan database <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">neurocare_ai</code> sudah ter-setup.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-secondary-blue text-[10px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Periksa file konfigurasi .env</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Pastikan variabel <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">PYTHON_API_URL</code>, <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">DB_HOST</code>, dan <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">DB_NAME</code> sudah diisi dengan benar.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-secondary-blue text-[10px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Restart server Node.js</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Hentikan server dan jalankan ulang dengan <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">npm run dev</code> atau <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">npm start</code>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-center text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-5">
                &copy; 2026 NeuroCare AI &mdash; Kelompok APM, Universitas Andalas
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
